      "title": "SLFP meets the President",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Its Chairman Maithripala Sirisena said that the Sri Lanka Freedom Party will meet President Ranil Wickramasinghe today to discuss an all-party government.",
        "Mr. Maithripala Sirisena said this at a press conference held today at the party headquarters."
